title: 10 Nenkan Tomodachida To Omotteta Otokonoko Ni Kokuhaku Sareru Ohanashi
description: A heartfelt story about a boy who believes he's too ordinary to attract attention, only to be confessed to by a girl after ten years of friendship. This manga explores themes of love, growth, and the beauty of genuine connections.

title: 20Th Century Boys
description: 20th Century Boys is a gripping manga that blends mystery, thriller, and science fiction as a group of childhood friends confront a dark conspiracy threatening the world, exploring themes of friendship, nostalgia, and the battle between good and evil.

title: 7 Nin No Nemuri Hime
description: 7 Nin No Nemuri Hime is a fantasy manga that follows the adventures of seven princesses with unique powers, battling dark forces to protect their kingdom. Filled with magic, bravery, and camaraderie, it offers a captivating story of heroism and friendship in a mystical world.

title: A Parallel World With A 1 39 Male To Female Ratio Is Unexpectedly Normal
description: In a parallel world where males vastly outnumber females, society adapts in surprising ways. This manga explores the daily lives, challenges, and unique dynamics of its inhabitants, blending fantasy elements with humorous and heartfelt moments in a remarkably normal setting.

title: A Story About A Man And A Woman And When They Sleep Together Money Appears Out Of Nowhere
description: A captivating manga exploring the unexpected romantic connection between a man and a woman, where their intimate moments mysteriously generate money. Blending romance with a touch of supernatural intrigue, it delves into themes of love, luck, and the strange consequences of their relationship.

title: A Story About Smoking At The Back Of The Supermarket
description: A thought-provoking manga exploring everyday life and human interactions behind the scenes at a supermarket, highlighting subtle social dynamics and personal stories in a quiet, reflective manner.

title: Ajin
description: Ajin is a dark fantasy manga about immortal beings known as Ajin who secretly exist among humans. The story follows a young man who discovers his own Ajin nature and must navigate a dangerous world filled with government conspiracies and moral dilemmas, blending supernatural elements with intense action.

title: Akanabe Sensei Wa Tereshirazu
description: Akanabe Sensei Wa Tereshirazu is a humorous manga that follows the amusing misadventures of a quirky teacher. Filled with witty jokes and lighthearted moments, it offers a delightful glimpse into school life and the humorous side of teaching.

title: Akazukin Ni Taberareta Okami
description: Akazukin Ni Taberareta Okami is a fantasy manga that follows the adventures of a wolf who is cursed to eat red riding hood. Combining magical elements with heartfelt storytelling, it explores themes of friendship, courage, and redemption in a whimsical world.

title: And Yet The Town Moves
description: And Yet The Town Moves is a charming slice-of-life manga that follows the daily lives and humorous adventures of a young girl and her friends in a small town, capturing the warmth and simplicity of everyday moments with wit and heart.

title: Another World In Japan
description: Another World In Japan is a captivating fantasy manga that transports readers to a mystical realm intertwined with Japanese culture. Filled with adventure, magic, and intriguing characters, it offers an immersive experience for fans of otherworldly stories and fantastical worlds.

title: Ao No Hako
description: Ao No Hako is a captivating fantasy manga that explores mystical worlds and magical adventures. It follows characters as they navigate enchanting realms filled with wonder, danger, and discovery, blending imaginative storytelling with compelling artwork to create an immersive reading experience.

title: Assassination Classroom
description: Assassination Classroom is a humorous and action-packed manga about a class of students tasked with killing their alien teacher, who threatens to destroy Earth. Blending comedy, school life, and moments of heartfelt growth, it explores themes of friendship, responsibility, and redemption.

title: Attack On Titan
description: Attack On Titan is a gripping fantasy series set in a world where humanity fights for survival against giant humanoid creatures known as Titans. It explores themes of freedom, fear, and sacrifice through intense battles and complex characters.

title: Awkward Senpai
description: Awkward Senpai is a humorous manga that explores the amusing and relatable moments of a shy, clumsy senior navigating daily life and interactions. Filled with lighthearted humor and charming characters, it offers a delightful glimpse into the comedic side of everyday situations.

title: Azumanga Daioh
description: Azumanga Daioh is a lighthearted comedy manga that follows the daily lives of a group of high school girls and their quirky teachers, highlighting humorous and heartwarming moments with charming characters and witty humor.

title: Azure Wants To Turn Me Into The Ideal Bf
description: Azure Wants To Turn Me Into The Ideal Bf is a romantic manga exploring the humorous and heartfelt journey of a protagonist striving to become the perfect boyfriend, blending comedy and heartfelt moments as relationships develop and personal growth unfolds.

title: Baki Rahen
description: Baki Rahen is a gripping manga that explores intense martial arts battles and the resilience of fighters. Filled with dynamic action and compelling characters, it delves into themes of strength, perseverance, and rivalry, captivating fans of combat sports and adrenaline-pumping stories.

title: Bakuman
description: Bakuman follows two young aspiring manga artists as they navigate the challenges of the manga industry, balancing creativity, ambition, and personal relationships to achieve their dreams of becoming successful manga creators.

title: Baroness Goes On Strike
description: Baroness Goes On Strike is a humorous manga that follows a noblewoman who decides to protest her mundane royal duties, leading to amusing situations and witty commentary on aristocratic life. It blends satire and comedy to entertain readers with its lighthearted take on noble society.

title: Be The Actor
description: Be The Actor is a captivating manga that explores the journey of aspiring performers as they navigate the challenges of the entertainment industry, showcasing their passion, talent, and perseverance in pursuit of stardom.

title: Beelzebub
description: Beelzebub is a humorous manga about a delinquent teen who is tasked with raising the demon lord baby Beelzebub. Filled with comedic battles and quirky characters, it blends supernatural elements with everyday school life for a lighthearted and entertaining story.

title: Berserk
description: Berserk is a dark fantasy manga that follows Guts, a lone mercenary with a tragic past, as he battles supernatural forces and human enemies in a brutal, medieval-inspired world. Known for its intense storytelling and intricate artwork, it explores themes of fate, revenge, and the struggle for survival.

title: Black Clover
description: Black Clover follows Asta, a boy born without magic in a world where magic is everything. Despite this, he dreams of becoming the Wizard King. Filled with magic battles, adventures, and friendship, it explores perseverance and determination in a fantastical setting.

title: Black Lagoon
description: Black Lagoon is an intense action-packed manga following a group of mercenaries navigating the dangerous underworld of Southeast Asia, blending gritty realism with high-stakes conflicts and complex characters.

title: Bleach
description: Bleach follows Ichigo Kurosaki, a teenager who gains soul-reaping powers and battles evil spirits called Hollows. Combining action, supernatural elements, and a rich world of spirits, it explores themes of friendship, duty, and identity in a captivating fantasy setting.

title: Blue Giant
description: Blue Giant follows the inspiring journey of a passionate jazz saxophonist who strives to reach greatness. Through his dedication and love for music, he faces challenges and grows both personally and artistically, capturing the spirit of perseverance and the pursuit of dreams.

title: Blue Rock
description: Blue Rock is a captivating manga that explores themes of adventure and friendship. It follows the journey of characters overcoming challenges in a mysterious world, blending elements of mystery and camaraderie to create an engaging story for readers seeking excitement and emotional depth.

title: Bocchi The Rock
description: Bocchi The Rock follows the story of Hitori Bocchi, a shy girl who dreams of making friends through her love of music. As she joins her school's band, she navigates social challenges with humor and determination, creating a heartfelt and comedic journey about friendship and self-discovery.

title: Bokurano
description: Bokurano is a thought-provoking manga about a group of children who unexpectedly become pilots of a giant robot, confronting moral dilemmas and the burdens of their new roles. It explores themes of sacrifice, responsibility, and the human condition in a dark, compelling narrative.

title: Captain Tsubasa
description: Captain Tsubasa is a classic sports manga that follows the journey of talented young soccer players as they strive to become the best in the world. Filled with exciting matches, inspiring teamwork, and memorable characters, it celebrates passion and perseverance in the sport of soccer.

title: Cardcaptor Sakura
description: Cardcaptor Sakura follows the adventures of Sakura Kinomoto, a young girl who discovers magical powers and must retrieve powerful Clow Cards to prevent chaos. Combining charming characters and enchanting magic, it is a beloved series blending fantasy, friendship, and adventure.

title: Chansaw Man
description: Chainsaw Man follows Denji, a young man who merges with a devil to fight evil spirits. Combining dark humor, intense battles, and emotional depth, the series explores themes of survival, ambition, and humanity in a gritty supernatural world.

title: Chi Chikyuu No Undou Ni Tsuite
description: Chi Chikyuu No Undou Ni Tsuite explores a fantastical world where the Earth's movements influence magic and life. The story follows characters navigating this mystical environment, revealing secrets of the planet's energy and their own destinies in a captivating adventure.

title: Chiikawa
description: Chiikawa is a charming manga about tiny, adorable creatures navigating everyday life with humor and warmth. Its lighthearted stories and cute characters make it a delightful read for fans of comedy and slice-of-life genres.

title: Chuuka Ichiban
description: Chuuka Ichiban is a manga that follows a young chef's adventures as he learns the art of Chinese cuisine, overcoming challenges and rivalries. Filled with delicious dishes and exciting culinary battles, it celebrates the passion and skill involved in gourmet cooking.

title: City
description: City is a gripping manga that explores urban life, its challenges, and the diverse stories of its inhabitants. Through vivid artwork and compelling narratives, it captures the vibrancy and complexity of city living, offering readers a window into the everyday adventures and struggles within a bustling metropolis.

title: Creyon Shin Chan
description: Creyon Shin Chan is a humorous manga featuring the mischievous adventures of Shin Chan. Filled with comedic antics and lighthearted moments, it offers a fun and entertaining experience for readers of all ages, highlighting everyday life through the humorous lens of Shin Chan's playful personality.

title: Dandadan
description: Dandadan is a manga blending supernatural elements with humor and action. It follows high school students who encounter ghosts and aliens, navigating bizarre adventures and friendships. The series combines fantasy and comedy, offering a thrilling and humorous exploration of otherworldly phenomena.

title: Darling Why Cant We Divorce
description: Darling Why Can't We Divorce explores the complex emotions and societal pressures surrounding divorce, focusing on a couple navigating their strained relationship. It delves into themes of love, conflict, and personal growth, offering a heartfelt look at the challenges of ending a marriage and finding new beginnings.

title: Death Note
description: Death Note is a psychological thriller about a high school student who gains a mysterious notebook that allows him to kill anyone by writing their name. As he seeks justice, a tense cat-and-mouse game ensues with a genius detective, exploring themes of morality, power, and justice.

title: Deep Water
description: Deep Water is a gripping manga that explores the mysterious depths of the ocean, blending adventure and suspense as characters uncover hidden secrets beneath the waves. Its captivating storytelling immerses readers in an underwater world full of danger, discovery, and intrigue.

title: Delicious In Dungeon
description: Delicious In Dungeon is a fantasy manga that combines adventure with culinary exploration. It follows a group of adventurers who venture into a dungeon to find ingredients for a feast, blending action with mouth-watering recipes and humorous moments, making it a unique and engaging culinary fantasy story.

title: Demon Slayer
description: Demon Slayer follows Tanjiro Kamado, a young boy who becomes a demon slayer after his family is slaughtered by demons. He embarks on a perilous journey to avenge his family and find a cure for his sister Nezuko, who has been turned into a demon, facing fierce enemies and uncovering dark secrets along the way.

title: Detective Conan
description: Detective Conan follows high school detective Shinichi Kudo, who is transformed into a child after being poisoned. Using his sharp intellect, he solves complex cases while searching for those responsible, all while maintaining his secret identity and navigating a world of suspense and intrigue.

title: Diamond No Ace
description: Diamond No Ace is a captivating sports manga that follows the journey of Eijun Sawamura, a talented pitcher aiming to lead his high school team to victory. Filled with intense matches, teamwork, and personal growth, it celebrates the spirit of baseball and perseverance.

title: Divine Delivery
description: Divine Delivery is a whimsical fantasy manga about a celestial messenger who delivers divine blessings to humans, navigating earthly challenges and moral dilemmas. Combining humor and adventure, it explores themes of faith, responsibility, and the magic hidden in everyday life.

title: Divorcie Se De Mim Marido
description: Divorcie Se De Mim Marido is a romantic manga exploring themes of love, heartbreak, and personal growth. It follows the story of a woman navigating her emotions and relationships after a divorce, offering heartfelt moments and emotional depth in a compelling narrative.

title: Doomsias Healing Sessions
description: Doomsias Healing Sessions follows a mystical healer who uses magical techniques to cure ailments and mend spirits. Set in a fantastical world, the story explores themes of compassion, magic, and personal growth as characters seek solace and healing through extraordinary powers.

title: Doraemon
description: Doraemon is a beloved manga about a robotic cat from the future who helps a young boy navigate life's challenges with futuristic gadgets, blending humor and imagination in a heartwarming adventure.

title: Dosanko Gyaru Is Mega Cute
description: Dosanko Gyaru Is Mega Cute is a lighthearted manga that follows the humorous and charming adventures of a lively Hokkaido girl, showcasing her quirky personality and everyday misadventures in a fun, relatable way.

title: Doukutsu Ningen
description: Doukutsu Ningen is a fantasy manga that explores the adventures of mysterious underground beings. It delves into their unique world, blending imagination with intriguing characters, offering readers a captivating journey beneath the surface.

title: Dr Stone
description: Dr. Stone is a science-themed manga that follows Senku Ishigami, a genius who awakens in a world where humanity has been petrified for thousands of years. Using his scientific knowledge, he aims to rebuild civilization and uncover the mystery behind the petrification event.

title: Dragon Ball Super
description: Dragon Ball Super continues the adventures of Goku and friends as they face powerful new foes, explore alternate universes, and unlock new levels of strength. Filled with epic battles, humor, and camaraderie, it expands the beloved Dragon Ball universe for fans old and new.

title: Drifters
description: Drifters is a fantasy manga where historical warriors are transported to a mystical world to battle against dark forces. Combining action, strategy, and myth, it explores epic conflicts and legendary characters in a richly imagined universe.

title: Drop
description: Drop is a heartfelt manga that explores the tender relationship between a young girl and her childhood friend. Through emotional moments and charming interactions, it captures the essence of youthful love and the bittersweet experiences of growing up.

title: Dungeon Nursery
description: Dungeon Nursery is a charming fantasy manga about a magical nursery where adventurers' children are cared for and trained. Filled with whimsical creatures and heartwarming moments, it explores themes of family, growth, and adventure in a mystical underground world.

title: Dungeon Sherpa Meikyuu Michisaki
description: Dungeon Sherpa Meikyuu Michisaki follows the adventures of a seasoned guide who helps explorers navigate treacherous dungeons. Combining elements of fantasy and adventure, the story highlights teamwork, strategy, and the thrill of discovery in a mystical underground world.

title: Eizouken Ni Wa Te Wo Dasuna
description: Eizouken ni wa Te wo Dasuna is a captivating manga about three high school girls who form an animation club. Their passion for creating fantastical worlds and overcoming challenges drives their journey into the world of animation, blending creativity, friendship, and imagination in a vibrant, inspiring story.

title: Enen No Shouboutai
description: Enen No Shouboutai, also known as Fire Force, follows firefighters with pyrokinetic abilities battling supernatural fires and uncovering dark conspiracies. Combining intense battles with teamwork and heroism, it offers a thrilling blend of action and supernatural elements in a vibrant, fiery world.

title: Eren The Southpaw
description: Eren The Southpaw is an inspiring manga that follows the journey of a talented young boxer overcoming challenges in the ring. It highlights themes of perseverance, dedication, and the pursuit of greatness in the world of competitive sports.

title: Eternally-Regressing-Knight
description: Eternally-Regressing-Knight follows a brave warrior trapped in a time loop, repeatedly reliving battles to protect his world. With each reset, he gains new insights and skills, striving to break free from his cursed fate while facing formidable foes and uncovering hidden truths.

title: Evangelion
description: Evangelion is a groundbreaking mecha anime series that explores psychological themes, existential questions, and complex character relationships set in a dystopian future. It combines intense battles with deep philosophical insights, making it a compelling blend of science fiction and emotional storytelling.

title: Even The Captain Knight Miss Elf Wants To Be A Maiden
description: A charming fantasy manga where a brave knight, Miss Elf, aspires to embody the grace and innocence of a maiden. Blending adventure with lighthearted humor, it explores themes of identity, bravery, and the desire for a simpler, more genuine life in a magical world.

title: Eyeshield 21
description: Eyeshield 21 is a thrilling sports manga centered around American football. It follows Sena, a shy high schooler who becomes the team's secret weapon, showcasing intense matches, teamwork, and personal growth as they strive for victory and glory on the field.

title: Fantasista
description: Fantasista is a manga centered around soccer, following the journey of a talented young player striving to become a professional. It explores themes of teamwork, perseverance, and passion for the sport, inspiring readers with its dynamic matches and heartfelt character development.

title: Fantasy Bishoujo Juniku Ojisan To
description: Fantasy Bishoujo Juniku Ojisan To is a humorous manga about two middle-aged men who magically transform into beautiful young women, leading to comedic and romantic adventures as they navigate their new identities and relationships in a fantastical world.

title: Flying Witch
description: Flying Witch is a charming slice-of-life manga that follows Makoto, a young witch-in-training, as she navigates everyday life, magic, and her new rural surroundings. It's a gentle, humorous series celebrating magic, friendship, and the simple joys of daily living.

title: Futari Solo Camp
description: Futari Solo Camp follows two friends as they embark on solo camping adventures, exploring the joys of outdoor life and friendship. The manga captures the peaceful moments of camping, nature, and personal growth, offering a relaxing and heartwarming experience for fans of outdoor and slice-of-life stories.

title: Futsu No Keionbu
description: Futsu No Keionbu is a lighthearted manga focusing on high school girls forming a band, exploring their friendships, musical pursuits, and everyday school life with humor and charm.

title: Gachiakuta
description: Gachiakuta is a gritty manga set in a dystopian world where underground fighting and survival are central themes. It explores the struggles of its characters as they navigate violence, loyalty, and hope amidst chaos, offering a raw and intense narrative that delves into human resilience.

title: Gan Kon
description: Gan Kon is a humorous manga that follows the comedic adventures of a young girl navigating everyday life with wit and charm. Filled with funny moments and lighthearted interactions, it offers a delightful escape into a world of laughter and fun.

title: Gantz
description: Gantz is a gripping sci-fi manga where characters are resurrected after death to participate in deadly missions against alien creatures, blending intense action with psychological and moral dilemmas in a dystopian future.

title: Ghost In The Shell
description: Ghost in the Shell is a cyberpunk manga set in a futuristic world where technology and humanity intertwine. It explores themes of identity, consciousness, and artificial intelligence through the story of a cyborg policewoman tackling cybercrime and existential questions.

title: Girl X Vampire
description: Girl X Vampire is a captivating fantasy manga that explores the mysterious relationship between a young girl and a vampire. Blending supernatural elements with emotional depth, it offers readers an engaging story filled with intrigue, romance, and adventure in a dark, enchanting world.

title: Girlfriend Lee Sang
description: Girlfriend Lee Sang is a heartfelt romantic manga that explores the tender relationship between Lee Sang and his beloved. Filled with emotional moments and charming interactions, it captures the essence of love and companionship in a relatable and engaging story.

title: Gokushufudou The Way Of The House Husband
description: Gokushufudou: The Way Of The House Husband is a humorous manga about a former yakuza boss who becomes a dedicated house husband, balancing domestic chores with his intimidating reputation. It blends comedy and slice-of-life elements to showcase his humorous everyday life and interactions.

title: Golden Kamuy
description: Golden Kamuy is a gripping adventure manga set in early 20th-century Hokkaido, following a war veteran and an Ainu girl as they hunt for a hidden treasure. Blending action, history, and cultural elements, it offers a thrilling journey through rugged landscapes and complex characters.

title: Golgo 13
description: Golgo 13 is a gritty manga centered around a professional assassin known for his precision and calm demeanor. It explores themes of espionage, danger, and moral ambiguity, offering intense action and suspense in a realistic, mature setting.

title: Grappler Baki
description: Grappler Baki is a martial arts manga that follows Baki Hanma as he trains and fights to become the strongest fighter in the world, facing powerful opponents and intense battles in a gritty, action-packed universe.

title: Gto
description: GTO (Great Teacher Onizuka) follows Eikichi Onizuka, a former gang member turned high school teacher, as he navigates the challenges of teaching and mentoring students with unconventional methods, blending comedy, drama, and heartfelt moments in a compelling story about growth and redemption.

title: Hadashi No Gen
description: Hadashi No Gen is a poignant manga depicting the harrowing experiences of a young boy during the Hiroshima atomic bombing, highlighting themes of survival, resilience, and the human cost of war through powerful storytelling and emotional depth.

title: Hagane No Rennkinjutsushi
description: Hagane no Rennkinjutsushi, also known as Fullmetal Alchemist, follows two brothers using alchemy to search for the Philosopher's Stone and restore their bodies. Set in a richly crafted fantasy world, it explores themes of sacrifice, redemption, and the pursuit of truth through action-packed adventures and deep moral questions.

title: Haikyuu
description: Haikyuu is a thrilling sports manga that follows the journey of a high school volleyball team. It explores themes of teamwork, perseverance, and rivalry as the players strive to reach the top and overcome personal and team challenges.

title: Hanma Baki
description: Hanma Baki is a martial arts manga focusing on intense combat and powerful fighters. It follows Baki Hanma as he trains and battles formidable opponents to become the strongest fighter in the world, blending action, rivalry, and adrenaline-fueled conflicts.

title: Hataraku Maou Sama
description: Hataraku Maou Sama follows the Demon Lord Satan who, after being defeated, ends up working at a fast-food restaurant in modern Tokyo. The series blends humor with fantasy elements as characters navigate everyday life and unexpected challenges in a humorous and relatable way.

title: Healing Life Through Camping In Another
description: Healing Life Through Camping In Another is a heartwarming manga that explores the joys of outdoor life, personal growth, and the healing power of nature. Follow characters as they find solace and friendship through camping adventures, blending everyday struggles with serene outdoor experiences.

title: Hellsing
description: Hellsing follows the secret organization Hellsing, led by Sir Integra Hellsing, as they battle supernatural threats, particularly vampires. The series combines dark fantasy, action, and horror elements, focusing on the powerful vampire Alucard's missions to protect England from supernatural evil.

title: Henkyo Mob Kizoku No Uchi Ni Totsuidekita Akuyaku Reijo Ga Mechakucha Dekiru Yoi Yome Nandaga
description: A fantasy tale about a noblewoman turned villainess who finds herself in a new world, navigating her role as a wife with unexpected skills and wit. Blending adventure and humor, it explores her journey of growth and self-discovery in a fantastical setting.

title: Higanjima
description: Higanjima is a dark fantasy manga that follows a young man who ventures to a mysterious island to find his missing brother, only to encounter deadly creatures and supernatural forces. It combines horror, adventure, and suspense in a gripping tale of survival and supernatural intrigue.

title: Highschool Of The Dead
description: Highschool of the Dead is a thrilling horror manga that follows a group of high school students battling zombies and surviving a catastrophic outbreak, blending intense action with moments of camaraderie and survival in a post-apocalyptic world.

title: Hikaru No Go
description: Hikaru No Go follows a young boy who discovers a centuries-old spirit of a Go master. As he learns the strategic game, he faces challenges that blend supernatural elements with personal growth, offering a captivating story about passion, rivalry, and self-discovery.

title: Himouto Umaru Chan
description: Himouto Umaru Chan is a humorous slice-of-life manga that follows the daily antics of Umaru Doma, a perfect high school girl who transforms into a lazy, junk food-loving otaku at home. The series highlights her humorous interactions with family and friends, blending comedy with relatable everyday moments.

title: Hokuto No Ken
description: Hokuto No Ken, also known as Fist of the North Star, is a post-apocalyptic martial arts manga following Kenshiro, a skilled fighter who uses deadly techniques to protect the weak and fight against tyrannical warlords in a devastated world.

title: Hotaru No Mori E
description: Hotaru No Mori E is a heartfelt manga set in a mystical forest where spirits and humans coexist. It explores themes of friendship, nature, and magic through enchanting stories that evoke wonder and nostalgia. Perfect for fans of fantasy and emotional storytelling.

title: How Heavy Are The Dumbbells You Lift
description: How Heavy Are The Dumbbells You Lift is a comedy and sports manga that follows high school girl Hibiki as she discovers the joys of weightlifting, learning about fitness, friendship, and self-improvement along the way.

title: Hunter Hunter
description: Hunter x Hunter is an adventurous manga following Gon Freecss as he seeks to become a Hunter, exploring mysterious worlds, facing dangerous foes, and uncovering hidden truths. It's a thrilling blend of action, fantasy, and complex character development that captivates readers with its intricate plot and imaginative universe.

title: I Became The Tyrant Of A Defense Game
description: A gripping fantasy tale where the protagonist becomes a powerful tyrant within a defense game universe, navigating strategic battles and political intrigue while exploring themes of power and redemption.

title: I M An Isekai Master
description: A captivating tale of a protagonist transported to a magical world, mastering various skills and facing epic challenges. Blending adventure and humor, it explores themes of power, growth, and friendship in a vibrant fantasy setting.

title: I Will Raise This Family To Greatness
description: A heartfelt story about a determined individual striving to build a prosperous and loving family, overcoming challenges and fostering strong bonds along the way. It emphasizes themes of perseverance, family values, and personal growth.

title: Ika Musume
description: Ika Musume follows the humorous adventures of a squid girl who vows to invade the Earth but ends up living with a human family, leading to comedic misunderstandings and quirky situations. The series blends humor with lighthearted moments, making it a charming slice of comedy about an unusual aquatic girl adapting to human life.

title: Inaka No Home Center Otoko No Jiyuu Na Isekai Seikatsu
description: Inaka No Home Center Otoko No Jiyuu Na Isekai Seikatsu is a fantasy manga about a man transported to a magical world where he seeks freedom and adventure, exploring new realms and forging alliances in a vibrant, fantastical setting.

title: Isekai Craft Gurashi Jiyu Kimamana Seisan Shoku No Honobono Slow Life
description: A relaxing story about a character living a slow, peaceful life while engaging in crafting and daily activities in a charming fantasy world. Emphasizing comfort and simplicity, it offers a soothing escape into a world of creativity and tranquility.

title: Isekai Ojisan
description: Isekai Ojisan follows the story of a man who is transported to a fantasy world and gains extraordinary powers, only to return to his original world with memories of his adventures. The manga blends humor, adventure, and fantasy elements, offering a unique take on the isekai genre with comedic and heartfelt moments.

title: Issak
description: Issak is a captivating fantasy manga that follows a young hero's journey through mystical realms, battling dark forces and uncovering ancient secrets. Rich in adventure and magic, it immerses readers in a world of wonder and heroism.

title: Jakdu
description: Jakdu is a martial arts manga centered around the traditional Korean combat sport. It follows the intense training, rivalries, and competitions of young fighters striving to excel in this disciplined and strategic martial art. The series highlights themes of perseverance, honor, and personal growth through dynamic fight scenes and character development.

title: Jibaku Shounen Hanako Kun
description: Jibaku Shounen Hanako Kun follows the supernatural adventures of Hanako, a ghostly spirit who grants wishes and solves mysteries in a haunted school. Blending humor, mystery, and supernatural elements, it explores the interactions between humans and spirits in a charming, eerie world.

title: Jigokuraku
description: Jigokuraku follows the story of a skilled ninja seeking the secret to eternal life while navigating a deadly island filled with monsters and mysteries. Blending dark fantasy and intense action, it explores themes of survival, morality, and the human desire for immortality.

title: Jin
description: Jin is a gripping sci-fi manga that follows a doctor who is transported back to ancient Japan, blending medical science with historical adventure. It explores themes of time travel, ethics, and survival, offering a compelling mix of action and drama in a richly detailed setting.

title: Jojo The Steel Ball Run
description: Jojo The Steel Ball Run is a thrilling manga set in a cross-country horse race across America, featuring supernatural abilities, intense battles, and unique characters. It combines action, adventure, and mystery, creating an engaging story that explores themes of perseverance and destiny.

title: Jujutsu Kaisen

It follows Yuji Itadori as he joins a secret organization to combat these malevolent entities using powerful jujutsu techniques, blending supernatural battles with compelling characters and dark, thrilling adventures.

title: Kaguya Sama Wa Kokurasetai

Their witty mind games and humorous misunderstandings create a charming story of love and pride, filled with clever banter and heartfelt moments.

title: Kaiju No 8
description: Kaiju No 8 follows the story of Kafka Hibino, who transforms from a monster-cleaning worker into a formidable hero fighting giant kaiju threats. Blending action, humor, and suspense, it explores themes of heroism and personal growth in a world besieged by monstrous creatures.

title: Kanojo No Sore Ni Yarareteru
description: Kanojo No Sore Ni Yarareteru is a heartfelt romance manga exploring the emotional struggles and growth of a young woman navigating love, relationships, and personal challenges in a touching and relatable story.

title: Kanojo Okarishimasu
description: Kanojo Okarishimasu follows Kazuya, a college student who rents a girlfriend after a breakup. As he navigates complex relationships and personal growth, the story blends humor, romance, and heartfelt moments, exploring themes of love, friendship, and self-discovery in a modern setting.

title: Kaoru Hana Wa Rin To Saku
description: Kaoru Hana Wa Rin To Saku is a heartfelt romance manga that explores the delicate emotions and blossoming love between its characters, set against a beautifully crafted backdrop. It captures the tender moments and emotional growth, making it a touching story for fans of romantic narratives.

title: Karakai Jouzu No Moto Takagisan
description: Karakai Jouzu No Moto Takagisan is a humorous manga that follows the amusing interactions between Takagi and Nishikata, classmates who engage in playful teasing and witty banter. The series highlights their lighthearted rivalry and friendship, delivering charming comedy and relatable school life moments.

title: Karakai Jouzu No Takagisan
description: Karakai Jouzu no Takagisan is a humorous manga about a high school girl who is secretly skilled at teasing her crush, leading to funny and endearing interactions. The series blends comedy with light-hearted romance, showcasing playful banter and charming character dynamics.

description: A young man trapped in a mysterious game world struggles to level up and uncover the secrets behind his stagnation. Combining adventure and supernatural elements, it explores themes of perseverance and hidden powers in a fantastical setting.

title: The Promised Neverland
description: The Promised Neverland is a suspenseful manga about children in a seemingly idyllic orphanage who uncover dark secrets and plan their escape. Combining mystery, psychological thriller, and survival elements, it explores themes of trust, intelligence, and resilience in a tense, gripping narrative.

title: The Regressed Mercenarys Machinations
description: A gripping fantasy tale following a mercenary who regresses in time, gaining new insights and powers. As they navigate a treacherous world filled with magic and danger, they seek to alter their fate and uncover hidden truths behind their past and the world's mysteries.

title: The Starts And I
description: The Starts And I is a captivating manga exploring personal growth and self-discovery. Through heartfelt storytelling and engaging characters, it offers a unique perspective on life's challenges and triumphs, making it a compelling read for those seeking inspiration and insight.

title: The Tale Of The Elixir In The Royal Capital
description: In the majestic royal capital, a young alchemist uncovers a mysterious elixir with the power to change destinies. Amid political intrigue and magical wonders, she embarks on a quest to unlock its secrets, blending adventure and enchantment in a captivating fantasy world.

title: The Weakest Slime I Once Saved Became The Strongest And Now Wont Leave My Side
description: A heartwarming fantasy tale about a kind-hearted hero who saves a weak slime, only to discover it becomes his strongest ally. Their bond grows stronger as they face adventures and challenges together, blending humor, magic, and friendship in a captivating story.

title: They Are Still Being Shaken This Morning
description: They Are Still Being Shaken This Morning is a reflective manga exploring everyday life and personal emotions. Through subtle storytelling and character interactions, it offers a gentle glimpse into ordinary moments that resonate deeply with readers seeking relatable, heartfelt narratives.

title: Toaru Majutsu No Index
description: Toaru Majutsu no Index is a fantasy adventure set in a world where magic and science coexist. It follows Kamijou Touma, a student with a mysterious power, as he encounters various magical factions and battles supernatural threats, blending action, mystery, and supernatural elements.

title: Tokyo Ghoul
description: Tokyo Ghoul follows Kaneki, a college student who becomes a half-ghoul after a deadly encounter. Navigating a dark, dangerous world of flesh-eating creatures and human conflicts, he struggles with his identity, survival, and the blurred lines between humanity and monstrosity.

title: Tokyo Revengers
description: Tokyo Revengers follows Takemichi Hanagaki as he time-travels to his middle school days to save his friends and prevent a tragic gang war, blending elements of action, drama, and supernatural time manipulation.

title: Toriko
description: Toriko is a culinary adventure manga that follows Gourmet Hunter Toriko as he searches for rare ingredients across fantastical worlds, facing dangerous creatures and challenges to create the ultimate dishes. It blends action, humor, and gastronomy in a flavorful story.

title: Toshokan No Daimajutsushi
description: Toshokan No Daimajutsushi is a fantasy manga that follows a young librarian with magical abilities who embarks on adventures to protect rare books and uncover ancient secrets, blending mystical elements with a captivating story of knowledge and bravery.

title: Tougen Anki
description: Tougen Anki is a fantasy manga that follows the adventures of a young hero wielding a mysterious sword. Set in a mystical world, it explores themes of courage, friendship, and magic as characters battle powerful foes and uncover ancient secrets.

title: Tsukkomi Machi No Machino San
description: Tsukkomi Machi No Machino San is a humorous manga that revolves around witty comebacks and comedic interactions in everyday life, highlighting the humorous side of social situations with sharp humor and lively characters.

title: Tsuyoshi
description: Tsuyoshi is a heartfelt story exploring everyday life and personal growth. It captures the subtle joys and struggles of its characters, offering a relatable and touching narrative that resonates with readers seeking a genuine slice-of-life experience.

title: Uchuu Kyoudai
description: Uchuu Kyoudai follows the inspiring journey of two brothers aspiring to become astronauts, exploring themes of dreams, perseverance, and sibling bonds. Set against a backdrop of space exploration, it offers a heartfelt and realistic portrayal of their challenges and triumphs.

title: Ultraman X Osomatsu San
description: Ultraman X Osomatsu San combines the thrilling alien battles of Ultraman with the comedic antics of Osomatsu San, creating a unique blend of science fiction and humor. The series features heroic fights against monsters alongside hilarious, everyday misadventures of the sextuplets, appealing to fans of both genres.

title: Ura Dungeon Okusan
description: Ura Dungeon Okusan is a humorous manga set in a fantastical world where a brave heroine explores mysterious dungeons, encountering quirky creatures and humorous situations. Its lighthearted tone and imaginative setting make it an entertaining read for fans of fantasy comedy.

title: Urusei Yatsura
description: Urusei Yatsura is a humorous and romantic manga that follows the misadventures of Ataru Moroboshi and the alien girl Lum. Filled with quirky characters and comedic situations, it blends romance, comedy, and sci-fi elements in a lively, entertaining story.

title: Ushio To Tora
description: Ushio To Tora follows the story of Ushio Aotsuki, a young boy who releases a powerful tiger-like demon trapped in a mysterious spear. Together, they face supernatural threats, forging a bond as they battle evil spirits and uncover ancient secrets in a thrilling fantasy adventure.

title: Usogui
description: Usogui is a psychological and strategic manga centered around high-stakes gambling. It follows Baku Madarame, a skilled gambler who faces dangerous opponents in intense games that test his wit and resolve. The series explores themes of risk, deception, and human nature in a gripping, suspenseful narrative.

title: Vagabond
description: Vagabond is a gripping manga that explores the life of the legendary swordsman Miyamoto Musashi. Through intense battles and personal growth, it delves into themes of honor, ambition, and the pursuit of mastery in a historical setting.

title: Vinland Saga
description: Vinland Saga is an epic historical manga that follows Thorfinn, a young Viking warrior, as he seeks revenge and explores themes of war, honor, and redemption in the Viking Age.

title: Wakabachan Wa Wakarasetai
description: Wakabachan Wa Wakarasetai is a humorous manga that follows the amusing daily life of Wakabachan, a lively and quirky girl. Filled with comedic moments and lighthearted interactions, it offers a fun and entertaining glimpse into her amusing adventures and relationships.

title: Warrior Of The Sword Heart
description: Warrior Of The Sword Heart is a captivating fantasy manga that follows a brave swordsman on a quest to save his homeland from dark forces. Filled with epic battles, mystical creatures, and heroic deeds, it immerses readers in a world of magic and adventure.

title: Warriors Life Logbook
description: Warriors Life Logbook is a captivating manga that explores the daily adventures and challenges of warriors in a fantastical world. Combining elements of action and adventure, it offers readers an engaging glimpse into the lives and battles of its heroic characters.

title: We Are Cats
description: We Are Cats is a humorous manga that follows the amusing adventures of a group of feline friends navigating their quirky daily lives, highlighting their playful antics and witty interactions in a charming and lighthearted story.

title: Weak Hero
description: Weak Hero follows the story of a timid high school student who, despite his frail appearance, confronts bullying and uncovers hidden strength. Combining intense battles with emotional depth, it explores themes of courage, friendship, and resilience in a gritty school setting.

title: Welcome Back Alice
description: Welcome Back Alice is a captivating fantasy manga that follows Alice's return to a magical world she once knew. Filled with adventure, mystery, and enchanting characters, it explores themes of friendship and self-discovery as Alice navigates her way through a realm of wonder and danger.

title: Welcome To Japan Ms Elf
description: Welcome To Japan Ms Elf is a charming fantasy manga that follows an elf navigating modern Japanese society. Blending magic with everyday life, it offers humorous and heartwarming moments as the protagonist explores new experiences and friendships in a vibrant, fantastical setting.

title: Welcome To The Nhk
description: Welcome To The NHK is a psychological and social commentary manga that explores the life of a hikikomori and his encounters with a mysterious girl. It delves into themes of loneliness, mental health, and societal pressures, offering a thought-provoking look at modern life and personal struggles.

title: Wolf Chan Wa Sumashitai
description: Wolf Chan Wa Sumashitai is a fantasy manga that follows the adventures of a wolf protagonist seeking companionship and understanding in a mystical world. Combining enchanting visuals with heartfelt storytelling, it explores themes of friendship, identity, and the magic that lies within us all.

title: World Trigger
description: World Trigger is a thrilling sci-fi manga set in a world where mysterious portals unleash invading monsters. A group of elite fighters, equipped with advanced weaponry and strategies, defend humanity from these threats while uncovering secrets behind the portals' origins.

title: Wotaku Ni Koi Wa Muzukashii
description: Wotaku Ni Koi Wa Muzukashii is a charming romantic comedy that explores the relationship between two adult friends who work in the same company. Their playful interactions and genuine emotions depict the complexities of love and friendship in a relatable, heartfelt manner.

title: Yachiru San Grows Praised
description: Yachiru San Grows Praised is a heartfelt story exploring personal growth and recognition. It delves into themes of perseverance and self-improvement, offering readers an inspiring journey through the protagonist's experiences and achievements.

title: Yaiba
description: Yaiba follows the adventurous young swordsman Yaiba Kamikaze as he battles supernatural foes and uncovers ancient mysteries. Combining action, humor, and fantasy elements, the manga offers an exciting journey through a world filled with mythical creatures and legendary battles.

title: Yajin Tensei Karate Survivoer In Another World
description: A martial artist is transported to a fantastical world where he must survive using his karate skills. Combining action and adventure, the story explores his battles, growth, and quest for survival in a realm filled with magic and monsters.

title: Yakitate Japan
description: Yakitate Japan is a comedic manga centered around baking bread, focusing on a young baker's quest to create the national bread of Japan. Filled with humor, culinary creativity, and competitive baking battles, it celebrates the art of bread-making and culinary passion.

title: Yamikin-Ushijima-Kun
description: Yamikin Ushijima-kun follows the gritty life of Ushijima, a debt collector navigating Japan's underworld. The series explores themes of crime, morality, and survival, offering a dark and intense look into the struggles faced by those on the fringes of society.

title: Yawara
description: Yawara is a sports manga centered around Judo, following the journey of a talented young girl as she trains and competes in tournaments. It explores themes of perseverance, discipline, and the pursuit of excellence in martial arts.

title: Yofukashi No Uta
description: Yofukashi No Uta, also known as Call of the Night, follows a teenage boy who becomes captivated by the night and encounters mysterious beings. Blending supernatural elements with coming-of-age themes, it explores the allure of darkness and the quest for connection in a world shrouded in mystery.

title: Yotsuba To!
description: Yotsuba To! is a charming slice-of-life manga that follows the everyday adventures of Yotsuba, a curious and energetic young girl. Through her innocent perspective, readers experience humorous and heartwarming moments in her lively, everyday world.

title: Yowamushi Pedal
description: Yowamushi Pedal is a thrilling manga about high school cycling. It follows the journey of Onoda Sakamichi and his teammates as they compete in intense races, showcasing teamwork, determination, and personal growth in the world of competitive cycling.

title: Zeikin De Katta Hon
description: Zeikin De Katta Hon explores the humorous and insightful world of finance and taxation, offering a unique blend of comedy and real-world issues. Through engaging storytelling, it provides a lighthearted look at the complexities of money management and fiscal policies, making finance accessible and entertaining for readers.

title: Zipang
description: Zipang is a manga that follows a modern Japanese Self-Defense Force ship that is transported back in time to World War II. The story explores themes of military strategy, historical events, and the moral dilemmas faced by the crew as they navigate a turbulent era.

title: Zombie Land Saga
description: Zombie Land Saga is a hilarious and unique anime that blends idol culture with zombie horror. It follows a group of undead girls brought back to life to revive Saga Prefecture through their singing and dancing, offering a quirky mix of comedy, music, and supernatural elements.
